<th><b>87</b></th>
<td><a href="/wiki/Berlin-Rahnsdorf_station" title="Berlin-Rahnsdorf station">S-Bhf. Berlin-Rahnsdorf</a> ↔ <a href="/wiki/Woltersdorf,_Brandenburg" title="Woltersdorf, Brandenburg">Woltersdorf</a> Schleuse (<i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Woltersdorf_Tramway&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Woltersdorf Tramway (page does not exist)">Woltersdorf Tramway</a></i>)</td>
