<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Reproductions">Reproductions</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trams_in_Berlin&amp;action=edit&amp;section=19" title="Edit section: Reproductions">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>You can find miniature replicas of various manufacturers in many scales. 1:24 scale replica exists manufactured by <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.occre.com/model-tram/berlin-tram.html">OcCre</a>.</p>
